skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: san francisco guide
des: This is a skill for San Francisco city guide. You can ask Alexa for an overview of San Francisco, top five things to do or some local news. This is a must-have skill for knowing more about the beautiful city of San Francisco. It can always keep you updated with the latest news around.
